node.text: L I M B S w/ @bryanna.creates
A thing I shot for a thing a while ago.

The people @DefJam and @Universalmusicgroup asked me to join @St.Bodhi to do a directors commentary of sorts on the #FlowerChild video I directed. Shout out to @Freenjoy and @Beingsinapars for producing and @yolandeg, @edithbo @nosteaksauce and #JeffBurroughs for always supporting wild ideas. All the thanks to Bodhi for trusting me with her music. Link to the full video in Bio. #StBodhi #ArketekMusic

Here are some frames from a video I did for @chaelincl a few years back. This is one of my favorites that sadly never saw the light of day. I was told by someone at her Korean label that I made her “look too powerful”. That was 100% my intention. I’m told that person is no longer employed there. Anyway it was a great time and CL performed flawlessly.  Hopefully one day our paths will cross again.  #CL #kpop #hellobitches
Happy birthday to the best Girlfriend a guy could ask for. ❤️ @bryanna.creates

A few stills I grabbed while directing the video for @fedez song #primadiognicosa late last year. When I first heard the song I for some reason thought of one my favorite photographers @crewdsonstudio and the way he lights his subjects. I wanted to channel some of those  moods into the video. @banksfilm did such a great job capturing the vibe and inspiration we were looking for. @fedez and @chiaraferragni had their son on set and in the video and it was an absolute pleasure to capture their lovely family.
